message.body: Moving day moving day!!! :D I get to see you soon!
Do you know when you are getting here? Do you need help moving?
Hey! Probably coming over in an hour or two. Wouldn't mind some help moving boxes up to my room, if you're up for it. Can't wait to see you! :)
Ok! I will finish eating and shower and head there. I know they are cleaning now anyway
Okay cool. I'll let you know when I'm heading over there.
